headline: Netflix gets a bullish call, AMC & Texas Instruments upgraded
summary: Yahoo Finance anchor Josh Lipton outlines the top stories on Wall Street on today's Market Minute. Netflix (NFLX) gets a bullish call by Needham analysts, saying the streaming giant stock could gain another 20%. AMC (AMC) stock gains after Wedbush upgraded the stock to Outperform. Texas Instruments (TXN) stock was also upgraded — to Buy from Hold by TD Cowen analysts. Stay up to date on the latest market action, minute-by-minute, with Yahoo Finance's Market Minute.
